1
00:00:06,306 --> 00:00:07,589
This is the toddler loop.

2
00:00:08,009 --> 00:00:09,954
A human classifies elements once.

3
00:00:10,394 --> 00:00:12,499
Clickable. Readable. Typable.

4
00:00:12,960 --> 00:00:15,005
The system learns the page vocabulary.

5
00:00:20,336 --> 00:00:21,897
Now watch what the agent sees.

6
00:00:22,478 --> 00:00:25,321
The sieve maps every interactive element
on the page.

7
00:00:25,841 --> 00:00:26,862
No language model.

8
00:00:27,323 --> 00:00:28,263
No vision model.

9
00:00:28,643 --> 00:00:29,524
Zero tokens.

10
00:00:30,803 --> 00:00:34,665
Product titles. Listing prices. Seller ratings.

11
00:00:35,146 --> 00:00:39,088
The agent scrolls down and the sieve
re-maps every new element instantly.

12
00:00:45,686 --> 00:00:47,033
A completely different site.

13
00:00:47,595 --> 00:00:49,466
A state park reservation system.

14
00:00:49,768 --> 00:00:51,398
The sieve maps it just the same.

15
00:00:51,639 --> 00:00:53,046
Any site. Any layout.

16
00:00:53,529 --> 00:00:54,515
Zero retraining.

17
00:00:57,966 --> 00:00:59,347
The sieve sees the page.

18
00:00:59,887 --> 00:01:01,689
The glossary names every element.

19
00:01:01,950 --> 00:01:04,852
Your agent knows what to click,
what to read, what to compare.

